arStrings.szText: Such heat... yet the town still stands. How long has it been burning?
To self. Wincing at the heat. Wary. (Suspects this fire isn't natural.)
Quelle chaleur… mais le village est toujours là. Depuis combien de temps brûle-t-il ?
